				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Battletoads often enables rendering partway into the screen. This requires the scroll position to be set by manually reloading the PPU address via $2006 before enabling the rendering, because it is too late for $2005 to set the scroll (which normally gets applied in the pre-render scanline). This could be a factor causing the screen to shake, depending on how you have implemented scrolling.</div>

